根据数据绘制初步条形图

# 设置细胞标识
seurat_ob <- SetIdent(seurat_ob,value = "celltype")

# 准备圈图绘图数据
# 由于原函数将降维方式写死为umap，我们的数据使tsne降维，这里修改一下函数
prepare_circlize_data = function (seu_obj, reduct="tsne",scale = 0.8){
    celltypes <- levels(seurat_ob)
    cell_colors <- (scales::hue_pal())(length(celltypes))
    data_plot <- get_metadata(seurat_ob, reductions = reduct,
                              color = cell_colors, coord_scale = scale)
    data_plot <- cell_order(data_plot)
    data_plot$x_polar2 <- log10(data_plot$x_polar)
    data_plot
}
# 准备圈图绘图数据
circ_data <- prepare_circlize_data(seurat_ob,reduct="tsne", scale = 0.8 )

set.seed(666)
# 设置细胞分群信息的颜色
cluster_colors<-rand_color(length(names(table(seurat_ob$seurat_clusters))))
celltype_colors<-rand_color(length(names(table(seurat_ob$celltype))))
rep_colors<-rand_color(length(names(table(seurat_ob$orig.ident))))

绘制细胞类型初步图形

# 绘制细胞类型圈图
plot_circlize(circ_data,do.label = T, pt.size = 0.3, col.use = celltype_colors,
              bg.color = 'white', kde2d.n = 200, repel = T)

添加背景颜色，设置标签字体大小

plot_circlize(circ_data,do.label = T, pt.size = 0.3, 
              col.use = celltype_colors ,
              bg.color = '#F9F1E1', 
              kde2d.n = 200, 
              repel = T, 
              label.cex = 0.8)

为圈图添加clusters和分组信息

# 绘制细胞分群圈图

plot_circlize(circ_data,do.label = T, pt.size = 0.5, col.use = celltype_colors ,
              bg.color = '#F9F1E1', kde2d.n = 200, repel = T, label.cex = 0.8)
# 添加细胞群注释信息
add_track(circ_data, group = "seurat_clusters", 
          colors = cluster_colors, track_num = 2) 
add_track(circ_data, group = "orig.ident",colors = rep_colors, track_num = 3)

读取亚型分析的数据结果

sub_celltype <- c("B cells","DC","Macro", "T cells")

sub.celltype_list <- sapply(sub_celltype,function(celltype){
  print(celltype)
  sub.celltype <- readRDS(paste0("data/sub",celltype,".rds"))
})

为图谱添加亚群分析结果

# 用B细胞尝试添加
B_cells <- sub.celltype_list[["B cells"]]
Idents(B_cells) <- "seurat_clusters"
set.seed(1234)
# 获取亚群颜色
subcolors <- rand_color(length(levels(B_cells)))
# 获取绘图数据
B_cells_meta<-get_metadata(B_cells, color = subcolors,reductions = "tsne")
# 获取各亚群中心点用于标记群
centers_B  <- B_cells_meta %>%  dplyr::group_by(seurat_clusters) %>%
              summarize(x = median(x = x),y = median(x = y)) 

# 可视化
plot_circlize(circ_data,do.label = T, pt.size = 0.5, col.use = celltype_colors ,bg.color = '#F9F1E1', kde2d.n = 200, repel = T, label.cex = 0.6)
# 添加细胞群注释信息
add_track(circ_data, group = "seurat_clusters", colors = cluster_colors, track_num = 2) 
add_track(circ_data, group = "orig.ident",colors = rep_colors, track_num = 3) 
# 添加亚群细胞
points(B_cells_meta$x*0.3-1.5, B_cells_meta$y*0.3+0.75, pch = 19, 
       col = alpha(B_cells_meta$Colors,0.5), cex = 0.1)
# 添加亚群细胞群标签（位置数值需要进行调试）
text(centers_B$x*0.3-1.5, centers_B$y*0.3+0.75,
     labels=centers_B$seurat_clusters, cex = 0.6, col = 'black')
# 添加亚群名称（位置数值需要进行调试）
text(x = quantile(B_cells_meta$x*0.3-1.5)[3],
     y = quantile(B_cells_meta$y*0.3+0.75)[5]+0.05,
     labels= "B cells",cex = 1, col = 'black')

批量计算并添加

# 批量获取绘图数据
celltype_meta <- lapply(sub.celltype_list,function(x){
  Idents(x) <- "seurat_clusters"
  subcolors <- rand_color(length(levels(x)))
  meta <- get_metadata(x, color = subcolors,reductions = "tsne")
  return(meta)
})
# 批量计算中心点
centers <- lapply(celltype_meta,function(x){
  center = x %>% dplyr::group_by(seurat_clusters) %>%
            summarize(x = median(x = x),y = median(x = y))
  return(center)
})

# 绘图
plot_circlize(circ_data,do.label = T, pt.size = 0.5, col.use = celltype_colors ,bg.color = '#F9F1E1', 
              kde2d.n = 200, repel = T, label.cex = 0.6)
# 添加细胞群注释信息
add_track(circ_data, group = "seurat_clusters", colors = cluster_colors, track_num = 2) 
add_track(circ_data, group = "orig.ident",colors = rep_colors, track_num = 3) 

# B细胞
points(celltype_meta[[1]]$x*0.4-1.5, celltype_meta[[1]]$y*0.4+0.75, pch = 19, 
       col = celltype_meta[[1]]$Colors, cex = 0.1)
text(centers[[1]]$x*0.4-1.5, centers[[1]]$y*0.4+0.75,
     labels=centers[[1]]$seurat_clusters, cex = 0.6, col = 'black')
text(x = quantile(celltype_meta[[1]]$x*0.4-1.5)[3],
     y = quantile(celltype_meta[[1]]$y*0.4+0.75)[1]-0.05,
     labels= "B cells",cex = 1, col = 'black')
# DC
points(celltype_meta[[2]]$x*0.4-1.5, celltype_meta[[2]]$y*0.4-0.75, pch = 19, 
       col = celltype_meta[[2]]$Colors, cex = 0.1)
text(centers[[2]]$x*0.4-1.5, centers[[2]]$y*0.4-0.75,
     labels=centers[[2]]$seurat_clusters, cex = 0.6, col = 'black')
text(x = quantile(celltype_meta[[2]]$x*0.4-1.5)[3],
     y = quantile(celltype_meta[[2]]$y*0.4-0.75)[5]+0.05,
     labels= "DC",cex = 1, col = 'black')
# Macro
points(celltype_meta[[3]]$x*0.4+1.5, celltype_meta[[3]]$y*0.4+0.75, pch = 19, 
       col = celltype_meta[[3]]$Colors, cex = 0.1)
text(centers[[3]]$x*0.4+1.5, centers[[3]]$y*0.4+0.75,
     labels=centers[[3]]$seurat_clusters, cex = 0.6, col = 'black')
text(x = quantile(celltype_meta[[3]]$x*0.3+1.5)[3],
     y = quantile(celltype_meta[[3]]$y*0.3+0.75)[1]-0.05,
     labels= "Macro",cex = 1, col = 'black')
# T细胞
